  {
    "tag": "blockquote",
    "innerHtml": "<p>\"The journey is done, the summit attained,<br>And the strong man must go.\"<br>\"I would hate that Death bandaged my eyes and forebore,<br>And bade me creep past.\"<br>\"No! let me taste the whole of it\"<br>\"The reward of all.\"  </p>"
